]], Germany\n|{{fb|Australia}}\n|align=\"center\" |1&nbsp;\u2013 0\n|align=\"center\" |1\u20130\n|[[2006 FIFA World Cup]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Roma'''<ref name=SW>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/francesco-totti/92/|title=F. Totti|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=18 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Serie A]]: [[2000\u201301 Serie A|2000\u201301]]\n*[[Coppa Italia]]: [[2006\u201307 Coppa Italia|2006\u201307]], [[2007\u201308 Coppa Italia|2007\u201308]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[2001 Supercoppa Italiana|2001]], [[2007 Supercoppa Italiana|2007]]\n\n'''Italy'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[FIFA World Cup]]: [[2006 FIFA World Cup|2006]]\n\n'''Italy Youth'''\n*[[Mediterranean Games|Mediterranean Games (Under-23)]]: [[1997 Mediterranean Games|1997]]\n*[[UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|UEFA European Under-21 Championship]]: [[1996 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1996]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n<!--LEAGUE AND FEDERATION-SANCTIONED AWARDS ONLY. No fan or magazine-voted awards. Listed in chronological order from last time won.-->\n*[[Guerin d'Oro]]: 1998, 2004<ref name=\"Guerin d'Oro\"/>\n*[[Serie A Young Footballer of the Year]]: 1999<ref name=\"OscarAIC\">{{cite web|url=http://www.storiedicalcio.altervista.org/storia-assocalciatori-sergio-campana_6.html|title=L'Associazione Italiana Calciatori (AIC): La Storia|publisher=Storie di Calcio|language=Italian|accessdate=25 November 2016}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Euro 2000 Final]]: Man of the Match<ref name=\"tattered international reputation\">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2006/jul/10/worldcup2006.sport2|title=Totti fails the final test and leaves a tattered international reputation|work=The Guardian|first=Jon|last=Brodkin|date=10 July 2006|accessdate=18 February 2017}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Euro 2000]]: [[2000 UEFA European Football Championship#Awards|Team of the Tournament]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/history/memories/newsid=1627525.html|title=UEFA Euro 2000 team of the tournament|publisher=UEFA|date=1 January 2011|accessdate=31 March 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Serie A Footballer of the Year]]: 2000, 2003<ref name=\"Guerin d'Oro\"/>\n*[[Serie A Italian Footballer of the Year]]: 2000, 2001, 2003, 2004, 2007<ref name=\"Oscar-del-Calcio\"/>\n*[[European Sports Media#ESM Team of the Year|ESM Team of the Year]]: [[European Sports Media#2000.E2.80.9301|2000\u201301]], [[European Sports Media#2003.E2.80.9304|2003\u201304]], [[European Sports Media#2006.E2.80.9307|2006\u201307]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/esm-xi.html |title=ESM XI |website=RSSSF |first=Karel |last=Stokkermans |date=14 March 2007 |accessdate=29 November 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207144925/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/esm-xi.html |archivedate=7 February 2016}}</ref>\n*[[FIFA 100]]<ref name=\"Pele\">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/3533891.stm|title=Pele's list of the greatest|work=BBC Sport|date=4 March 2004|accessdate=15 June 2013}}</ref>\n*[[Oscar del Calcio#Serie A Goal of the Year|Serie A Goal of the Year]]: 2005, 2006<ref name=\"Oscar-del-Calcio\"/>\n*[[2006 FIFA World Cup]] [[2006 FIFA World Cup#All-star team|All-Star Team]]'''<ref name=\"France, Italy dominate World Cup all-star squad\">{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/france-italy-dominate-world-cup-all-star-squad-1.572395|title=France, Italy dominate World Cup all-star squad|publisher=CBC Sports|date=7 July 2006|accessdate=27 May 2015}}</ref>\n*[[2006 FIFA World Cup]]: [[2006 FIFA World Cup#Assists|Assist Leader]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://soccer-europe.com/Archives/WorldCup/WorldCup2006/GoalsandAssists.html|title=2006 FIFA World Cup Goals & Assists|publisher=Soccer-Europe|accessdate=30 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Serie A]] Assist Leader: [[1998\u201399 Serie A|1998\u201399]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.football-lineups.com/tourn/Serie_A_1998-1999/stats/top_goal_scorers/|title=Serie A 1998/99 Stats|publisher=Football-Lineups.